{"tid":230782,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要買樓唔租樓，呢張單可以話到俾你知..","createTime":"2017-05-05T15:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T08:42:18.000Z","uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b61e8a3838e71394c2f626c1f78dc64908e22d5a","tid":230782,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:09:56.000Z","msg":"收到銀寄黎嘅通知書，啲人又話加息，點知通知我修訂後減左息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過呢個唔係重點，重點係去到最後一期還款，2045年11月26日，都只係同今日差唔多<br />\n<br />\n如果租樓，我唔知會被加租幾多囉，到時可能因為通賬每月用3，4萬交租，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2045年時1萬4一個月，房署嘅公屋都唔知租唔租到喇，點解啲人唔識計數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_170505/20170505_7b757a269805448d8aff2AWSybRNqHEH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_170505%2F20170505_7b757a269805448d8aff2AWSybRNqHEH.jpg&h=9d0a1f7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7bb9877bac302772655b879ac8efe4f810ddb4d","tid":230782,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"屌你咩"},{"pid":"07f415fde140c84bd763b881f3f2141026f8cea0","tid":230782,"uid":44044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:12:41.000Z","msg":"2045年.... 仲有28年加油！"},{"pid":"4121d1f7a6521df1eec6f0c727f170a199b3ab42","tid":230782,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ht0Q98V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHt0Q98V.jpg&h=624c4e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ee4d46c14069eff877685106090518f25e1028","tid":230782,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2045年.... 仲有28年加油！</blockquote><br />\n租樓租到六十歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32190a1af78696995f5e45dc680281aa477eecb4","tid":230782,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:33:41.000Z","msg":"有40% 係利息？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090b925a34c3bad1f07c6d409173b7073be31a6b","tid":230782,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"淡淡： 預計啫，唔比加P 既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cbec8d12c5cd41a6db0dd21512f9491a227e0a","tid":230782,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:39:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有40% 係利息？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本金同利息六四比好平常，之後利息比例就越供越少"},{"pid":"22e1c38638352a143a72d1a0e6a0b8b92ff1ea1d","tid":230782,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有40% 係利息？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好正常吖，通常唔會供30年，十零年好多贖咗樓，咁銀行前面緊係息多本少，唔係早咗贖樓咪賺少咗"},{"pid":"aff40aedd6c04bd87905bfce7cdb4cc31d9e439c","tid":230782,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2045年.... 仲有28年加油！</blockquote><br />\n如果你有層供完既樓講呢句無咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f567f2137c74223249290b24a2a6313aadc3d4","tid":230782,"uid":58277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"點解而家啲